moa.classifiers.multilabel

Class MajorityLabelset

  • java.lang.Object
    • moa.AbstractMOAObject
      • moa.options.AbstractOptionHandler
        • moa.classifiers.AbstractClassifier
          • moa.classifiers.AbstractMultiLabelLearner
            • moa.classifiers.multilabel.MajorityLabelset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable, Serializable, Classifier, MultiLabelLearner, MultiTargetRegressor, AWTRenderable, Learner<Example<Instance>>, MOAObject, OptionHandler

    public class MajorityLabelset
extends AbstractMultiLabelLearner
implements MultiTargetRegressor
    Majority Labelset classifier. Each labelset combination of relevances, e.g. [0,0,1,1,0,0], is treated as a single class value.
